Jacqueline Wolper Massawe a mụrụ na 18 Disemba 1987, bụ onye Tanzania na-eme ihe nkiri na onye na-emepụta ejiji
Wolper malitere ọrụ ihe nkiri ya n'afọ 2007 ma gosipụta ihe karịrị ihe nkiri 30 kemgbe mmalite ya.
A mụrụ Wolper ma zụlite ya na Moshi, Tanzania. Ọ gara Mawenzi Primary School tupu ọ kwaga Magrath, Ekenywa na Masai maka ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị ya
O mechara gụọ asụsụ na ICC Arusha na ọmụmụ azụmahịa ndị ọzọ.
Wolper banyere na ụlọ ọrụ ihe nkiri nke Tanzania n'afọ 2007 ebe onye na-eme ihe nkiri Lucy Komba chọpụtara ma mee ka o kwenye isonye na ụlọ ọrụ fim
Wolper na-arụ ọrụ na salon ya ebe Lucy bụ otu n'ime ndị ahịa ya

Ọ pụtara na mbụ na ihe nkiri nke Lucy Komba Ama Zako Ama Zangu ebe ọ rụrụ ọrụ dị ka odeakwụkwọ. O mechara pụta n'otu ebe Steven Kanumba na onye isi ya bụ Mtitu Game nwere mmasị n'ebe ọ nọ ma tinye ya na Family Tearsá na Red Valentineá
Ihe nkiri ya ndị ọzọ gụnyere Kipenzi Changu, Family Tears, Red Valentine, Surprise, Chaguo Langu, Candy, Taxi Driver na ọtụtụ ndị ọzọ.
Wolper malitere ịkpa onye egwu a ma ama bụ Harmonize n'ọnwa Mee afọ 2016

Otú ọ dị, ha abụọ kewara n'ọnwa Febụwarị afọ 2017. Ya na onye egwu ya, Diamond Platnumz nwekwara mmekọrịta. N'agbanyeghị na ọ nwere mmasị na omenala Kenya, Wolper kwuru na ọ chọghị ka ya na nwoke Kenya nwee mmekọrịta.
N'afọ 2018, ọ mara ọkwa na ọ ghọwo Onye Kraịst a mụrụ ọzọ. A maara Wolper maka nkwupụta esemokwu ya na mgbasa ozi Tanzania, ọ kwupụtakwara egwu na a ga-eme ya n'ihi ha.
